title: The Coordinators
overview: In their realm of possibility, only in death can there can be life. As such, life after death has become the mantra of organ donation coordinators.After nurse Wen Yu Dou helps in the successful delivery of the 1000th baby in her charge, she changes her career path to join the organ donor coordinators where she meets Jiang Jun Hao, a rising star in the field of surgery who is obsessed with Star Trek. They take on difficult cases time and again and also unexpectedly find love.
